80
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:50,620
S-Stupid skeleton! B-Beat it already!

81
00:05:50,620 --> 00:05:52,910
Evil be gone! Evil be gone!

82
00:05:52,910 --> 00:05:53,700
H-Hey...

83
00:05:53,910 --> 00:05:56,660
Wow, it's working! Usopp, that's amazing!

84
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:58,420
"Evil Be Gone"

85
00:05:57,540 --> 00:06:02,250
You know it! This is my full
"Anti-Evil Spirit Arsenal."

86
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,590
An evil spirit?! Where? Where is it?

87
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,550
--It's you!
--What?!

88
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:12,760
Damn it! There's no way a skeleton
can walk, talk, and grow an afro!

89
